OL,3,CFamily take fight for law in name of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler to parliament
OL,6,FA family's fight for a new law in the
OL,7,Fname of murdered toddler Maya Chappell
OL,8,Fhas been debated in parliament.
OL,10,FMaya was two years old when she
OL,11,Fsuffered severe brain damage and died
OL,12,Fafter being shaken by her mother's
OL,13,Fboyfriend in Shotton Colliery in 2022.
OL,15,FOn Tuesday (14 October), the little
OL,16,Fgirl's family's campaign for Maya's
OL,17,FLaw was raised in parliament by MP Liz
OL,18,FTwist.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/10
