OL,3,CFamily take fight for law in name of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler to parliament
OL,6,FThe family hope the law would allow
OL,7,Fparents or guardians of children to
OL,8,Faccess information about the known
OL,9,Frisks of non-sexual abuse of new care-
OL,10,Fgivers.
OL,12,FGemma Chappell and Rachael Walls,
OL,13,FMaya's great aunts, travelled to
OL,14,FLondon for the debate.
OL,16,FSpeaking to ITV Tyne Tees, Gemma said:
OL,17,F"It's not just about Maya, it's about
OL,18,Fall the other children that have gone
OL,19,Fthrough this, and the children that
OL,20,Fare going through it now.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
