OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F428A1760652516
OL,3,CFamily take fight for law in name of
OL,4,Cmurdered toddler to parliament
OL,6,F"It's important to give not just Maya
OL,7,Fa voice, but for Maya's voice to be
OL,8,Fthe voice of the children that have
OL,9,Fgone through it, but the voice of the
OL,10,Fchildren that are going through it
OL,11,Fnow."
OL,13,FMaya was violently shaken by her
OL,14,Fmother's partner, Michael Daymond, and
OL,15,Fdied from severe brain trauma.
OL,17,FDaymond was sentenced to life for
OL,18,Fmurder, while her mother Dana Carr is
OL,19,Fserving nine years in prison for
OL,20,Fneglect and allowing the death of a
OL,21,Fchild.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
