OL,6,FGemma says her nephew James, Maya's
OL,7,Ffather, had concerns about his
OL,8,Fdaughter's welfare in the lead up to
OL,9,Fher death.
OL,11,FShe said he tried to raise concerns
OL,12,Fwith services, but they were not taken
OL,13,Fseriously enough.
OL,15,FFollowing Maya's death, Gemma said it
OL,16,Femerged that Daymond had a history of
OL,17,Fdrug use, owed money and had history
OL,18,Fof abuse towards other women.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
