OL,4,Cmurdered toddler to parliament
OL,6,FCurrent laws allow you to find out if
OL,7,Fsomeone has a record of child sex
OL,8,Foffences, or if your partner has a
OL,9,Fhistory of domestic abuse.
OL,11,FMaya's family are pushing for new
OL,12,Flegislation which would specifically
OL,13,Ffocus on child abuse and neglect, and
OL,14,Fpotentially raise the alarm about care-
OL,15,Fgivers who pose a risk to children.
OL,17,FHer family believe this could have
OL,18,Fsaved her life while campaigners hope
OL,19,Fit will ensure children do not fall
OL,20,Fthrough the cracks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
