OL,6,FGemma added: "This affects everybody.
OL,7,FIt doesn't just affect us. We haven't
OL,8,Fgot an invisible cloak.
OL,10,F"It's happened to our family. It
OL,11,Fhappens to people in your street, in
OL,12,Fyour community, it happens all the
OL,13,Ftime. There are 59 children that are
OL,14,Fkilled each year at the hands of
OL,15,Fparents and carers."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
