OL,6,FDuring the debate in Westminster Hall
OL,7,Fon Tuesday afternoon, Labour MP for
OL,8,FBlaydon and Consett, Ms Twist, said:
OL,9,F"We need greater awareness amongst the
OL,10,Fpublic and professionals of
OL,11,Fsafeguarding risks that fall outside a
OL,12,Fnarrow view of sexual abuse and
OL,13,Fintimate partner violence.
OL,15,F"We need to support safeguarding
OL,16,Fagencies to fulfil their obligations
OL,17,Fand hold them to account, when these
OL,18,Fobligations are not fulfilled.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
