OL,6,F"And we need to close gaps to protect
OL,7,Fvulnerable children from slipping
OL,8,Fthrough the cracks of a fragmented
OL,9,Fsystem."
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FJosh MacAlister, Children and Families
OL,17,FMinister, described Maya's death as a
OL,18,Ftragedy and paid tribute to her great
OL,19,Faunts for their "tireless campaigning".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
