OL,6,FHe said: "We need fundamental change -
OL,7,Fwhich we are delivering, I believe,
OL,8,Fnow, through the most significant
OL,9,Foverhaul of children's social care in
OL,10,Fa generation - backed by legislative
OL,11,Fchange and over #2bn of investment in
OL,12,Fthis spending review period.
OL,14,F"Through these reforms, we are laying
OL,15,Fthe foundation for much better
OL,16,Finformation sharing, introducing a
OL,17,Fresponsive family help system, and
OL,18,Fthirdly significantly sharpening up
OL,19,Four children protection arrangements.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
